divs: Sighting DetailsDriving north on Hiway 81 after crossing Bass Lake Road noticed a bright blinking red light to the west, also saw to the left and upper and lower of object there were blinking white lights. Pulled over on HiWay 81 got out of car and watched for about 2 minutes, now only seeing one object and it was round and had white rotating blinking lights all around it. Went home and got the camera and it was gone. My wife driving, my son in the back seat and we all saw the same thing.
Summary: Red blinking light - became a round object with blinking white lights all around it.
